  "name": "RPlog_A_Bad_Start_with_Ozzle",
  "title": "A Bad Start with Ozzle",
  "summary": "In the rain-soaked Fountain Square of Plaxton City on Caspar, the arrogant Imperial officer Joir arrives with two bodyguards in the wake of recent violence and seeks out the Dark Jedi Ozzle Olumpari, a gaunt Sarian he has observed before. Joir opens with a thinly veiled claim that the two share a common friend now in grave danger, but Ozzle, weary and prickly, rebuffs his imperious tone and demands he state his business plainly. As bystanders such as Tequa and Resniz trade rumors of the day's events around the square, the two men spar verbally, each probing the other's strength. Joir finally reveals that Ambassador Morganna Tazecks has been shot, along with a Sarian child, by a gunman already known to Imperial security for threatening her. The revelation visibly shakes Ozzle, who had been unaware of the attack, setting an uneasy tone for whatever alliance might follow.",
